Package com.fastasyncworldedit.core.math

Class LocalBlockVector2Set

java.lang.Object
com.fastasyncworldedit.core.math.LocalBlockVector2Set
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<BlockVector2>, Collection<BlockVector2>, Set<BlockVector2>
public class LocalBlockVector2Set extends Object implements Set<BlockVector2>
The LocalBlockVector2Set is a Memory and CPU optimized Set for storing BlockVector2s which are all in a local region - All vectors must be in a 65534 * 65534 area centered around the first entry - This will use 8 bytes for every 64 BlockVector2s (about 600x less than a HashSet)
Since:
2.13.0
